  <div class="article-content">
    <p>
      Living in Indiana with my wife Alyssa and our family. She's working through her accelerated nursing program at Purdue, and I'm the stay-at-home dad keeping things running on the home front.
    </p>

    <p>
      Volunteering with the local fire department as an EMT and firefighter. Still learning, still showing up.
    </p>

    <p>
      Rebuilding this website from WordPress to a static site stack (Astro + Vercel), with the goal of writing more — essays on technology, society, and whatever else is on my mind.
    </p>

    <p>
      Practicing piano. Beginner level, but consistent.
    </p>

